description._content: Title: Early Nord Pacific Creator: Kadel & Herbert, N.Y. Date: ca. 1912-1914 Place: France Part Of: David Goodyear collection of foreign railroad photographs Description: This first of the Nord Pacifics and the first locomotive of the small series 3.1151, 3.1170 is shown here in its original, unmodified state. Source: Collyns, Adrian H. Northern Steam Vapeurs du Nord. DeGolyer Library, Southern Methodist University, 2003. Physical Description: 1 photograph: black and white; 13 x 20 cm. File: ag1983_0266_24_01_07r_early_sm_opt.jpg Rights: Please cite Southern Methodist University, Central University Libraries, DeGolyer Library when using this image file. A high-quality version of this file may be obtained for a fee by contacting degolyer@smu.edu.
